00:19:57.932 --> 00:19:59.332 position:13% line:89% align:start
Mikey just shut your mouth.

00:20:00.500 --> 00:20:02.704 position:19% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] Mikey's
right though, actually.

00:20:02.737 --> 00:20:04.639 position:21% line:83% align:start
They're not the ones
who hurt this girl.

00:20:04.672 --> 00:20:08.375 position:21% line:83% align:start
Our poor daughter, in
a coma for days now!

00:20:11.179 --> 00:20:12.880 position:27% line:89% align:start
Just look at her!

00:20:12.914 --> 00:20:17.652 position:13% line:83% align:start
Her face and her body have
been battered and bruised!

00:20:17.685 --> 00:20:19.854 position:38% line:89% align:start
(sobbing)

00:20:21.756 --> 00:20:23.524 position:33% line:89% align:start
And for what?

00:20:23.558 --> 00:20:26.527 position:13% line:83% align:start
What did she ever do to you
to deserve such cruel abuse?

00:20:28.730 --> 00:20:30.932 position:30% line:89% align:start
(mother crying)

00:20:30.965 --> 00:20:33.201 position:16% line:89% align:start
Our beautiful little girl

00:20:33.233 --> 00:20:36.336 position:19% line:83% align:start
has been disfigured
and despoiled for life!

00:20:36.369 --> 00:20:38.606 position:5% line:89% align:start
You scum have ruined everything.

00:20:42.309 --> 00:20:43.644 position:33% line:89% align:start
Please leave.

00:20:43.678 --> 00:20:46.848 position:16% line:83% align:start
We never want to see you
here or anywhere again.

00:20:53.688 --> 00:20:56.157 position:7% line:89% align:start
Soon we'll be fighting Moebius.

00:20:56.190 --> 00:20:58.325 position:27% line:83% align:start
We'll deal with
our own problems,

00:20:58.358 --> 00:21:00.393 position:7% line:89% align:start
but it'll be in our own world.

00:21:01.361 --> 00:21:04.264 position:19% line:83% align:start
All of our crew have
families and relatives

00:21:04.297 --> 00:21:06.667 position:24% line:83% align:start
and people who are
important to them.

00:21:06.701 --> 00:21:09.771 position:10% line:83% align:start
We can't let innocent people
get dragged into this.

00:21:09.804 --> 00:21:11.773 position:24% line:83% align:start
We can't hurt their
friends and family.

00:21:13.241 --> 00:21:15.408 position:19% line:83% align:start
It's not that you
have to bow your head.

00:21:16.309 --> 00:21:18.311 position:10% line:89% align:start
Just have a heart that cares.

00:21:21.849 --> 00:21:23.350 position:16% line:89% align:start
You're a good guy, Kenny.

00:21:24.585 --> 00:21:26.486 position:13% line:89% align:start
You're right, I apologize,

00:21:27.655 --> 00:21:30.958 position:21% line:83% align:start
and I'm glad to
have you by my side.

00:21:34.662 --> 00:21:37.064 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] I think
now I can understand

00:21:37.098 --> 00:21:40.067 position:10% line:83% align:start
why Mikey would have changed
so much after Draken died.

00:21:41.334 --> 00:21:44.071 position:19% line:83% align:start
And how the Toman of
12 years in the future

00:21:44.105 --> 00:21:45.907 position:24% line:83% align:start
became such an
evil organization.

00:21:47.508 --> 00:21:49.877 position:19% line:83% align:start
Draken was never
supposed to have died.

00:21:51.279 --> 00:21:53.247 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] Draken
is Mikey's heart.

00:21:53.281 --> 00:21:55.516 position:24% line:83% align:start
He compensates for
what Mikey lacks.

00:21:58.418 --> 00:22:00.487 position:16% line:83% align:start
I'm feeling pretty hungry
all of a sudden, Kenny.

00:22:00.521 --> 00:22:03.558 position:16% line:83% align:start
What? You just chowed
down a whole kid's meal.

00:22:03.591 --> 00:22:05.358 position:5% line:89% align:start
I always get hungry after a nap.

00:22:05.392 --> 00:22:07.394 position:27% line:83% align:start
[Draken] How does
that even work?

00:22:08.629 --> 00:22:10.965 position:21% line:83% align:start
[Takemichi] If only
Naoto could see this.

00:22:10.998 --> 00:22:12.133 position:24% line:89% align:start
I knew I was right!

00:22:12.166 --> 00:22:14.035 position:24% line:83% align:start
There's just no
way that these two

00:22:14.068 --> 00:22:15.536 position:10% line:89% align:start
could ever fight each other!

00:22:17.905 --> 00:22:20.808 position:21% line:89% align:start
(closing theme music)

00:22:27.315 --> 00:22:31.986 position:24% line:83% align:start
(vocalists singing
in Japanese)

